column5: seems legit lol, huge muskie man thats great
lol turned a 10lber into a 20lber.......nice  thanks for the compliment (10lber)
with practice and new tricks she will make you world class fisherman  she has to watck that the pixels don't get too big
wow, you're good Terry, that's so good I have to question some of your fish pictures (hahaha)
the fish was too long so I had to make what you were standing on a bit bigger and add the rest of your boot   yeah I don't fish  I just photoshop fish into my pictures  and never trust my backgrounds

Now you won't need to go fishing at all. Just stand up with some bushes in the background and she can photoshop in whatever size and species you'd like!! No more dirty, smelly fingers from worm guts and roe juice ---eeeewww!!
Roe juice and worm poop!!  I think I might quit fishing because of this.
Must be a 12 step prog out there somewhere!!
Photoshop can be fun...especially when you playing with wild life and fish
You guys are demented and some of the reasons I come back everyday. LOL
Never have I seen such realism Chris.  You are a true talent in the dark room.  Your photofinishing is beyond any need for further practice.  I wish to God I could catch muskie like that.
Thats cool.. Ya im going to be looking real close at all your reports....lol
